name: Uirapuru
description:
Known as a magical bird, whoever finds it may have a special wish fulfilled. Uirapuru is a symbol of happiness. Legend has it that a young warrior fell in love with the wife of the great chief.
Because it was a forbidden love he couldn't get close to her. Therefore, he asked the god Tupã to transform him into a bird.<Crypto Legends | A Series by Renancio Monte | 2021>
